Application.Domain

Class Administrator

  • java.lang.Object
    • Application.Domain.Credentials
      • Application.Domain.Administrator

  • @Entity
public class Administrator
extends Credentials
    Administrator is the class that maps the database Entity Administrator. An Administrator is a user that manages the Scenario(s).
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Corti Lorenzo, Tocchetti Andrea
